# ROM/patch binaries — never commit copyrighted material
rom/*.gbc
rom/*.gb
rom/*.zip
*.gbc
*.gb
*.ips
*.ups
*.bps
build/
__pycache__/
*.pyc

# RGBDS is a third-party toolchain (github.com/gbdev/rgbds), not our code
tools/rgbds/

# pret/pokecrystal clone — third-party donor (species ids, routine labels,
# used for vanilla-Crystal build + bindiff), regenerable via git clone, not our code
tools/pokecrystal_donor/

# Ghidra install(s) + analysis project — huge, regenerable, not our code.
# Two coexist here: tools/ghidra_11.4.2/ (matches GhidraBoy's last officially
# supported version) is separate from Unbound/RadicalRed's tools/ghidra/
# (12.0.2, used for GBA work) because GhidraBoy doesn't build against 12.0.2
# (confirmed 2026-07-12 - Ghidra's AbstractProgramLoader API changed between
# 11.x and 12.x) - see docs/TOOLCHAIN.md.
tools/ghidra/
tools/ghidra_*/
tools/ghidraboy_src/
ghidra_project/

# local compiled/copied tool binaries — regenerate via build steps, not committed
tools/bin/

# venv for bsdiff4 (bindiff tooling) — regenerable via
# `python3 -m venv tools/bindiff_venv && tools/bindiff_venv/bin/pip install bsdiff4`
tools/bindiff_venv/

# venv for PyBoy (dynamic analysis / autoplay rig) — regenerable via
# `python3 -m venv tools/emu_venv && tools/emu_venv/bin/pip install pyboy`
tools/emu_venv/

# PyBoy savestates + progress screenshots — ROM-derived, never commit
tools/emu_states/

# Ghidra project for the Prism ROM (imported ROM copy inside) — ROM-derived
tools/ghidra_prism_proj/

docs/strings_dump.txt
docs/ghidra_analysis.log
docs/all_strings_dump.txt
docs/all_strings_dump.stderr

# Note: tools/character_mode/cache/ (scraped Bulbapedia/Rijon Wiki page cache)
# is intentionally NOT ignored, matching the Unbound/RadicalRed precedent —
# it's committed so a fresh clone doesn't need to re-scrape from scratch.

# Local Claude Code handoff notes (kept out of the public repo)
CLAUDE.md
